												"val": {
													"type": 23,
													"value": "[Player] Grab the Nerve and slowly connect them. Then pinch it like in the BG3 trailler <SimonG>, [Nerve Plane Tentacles] S_NervePlaneTentacles <- New rigged obj <SimonG>"
												}
